data.description: This 2500 s.f., 4-bd 2.5 bath home is on a .7 acre lot. Open porch on the front covered by the main roofline; A screened porch on the back, covered by a shingled roof with tile floors. As you enter the front, there's a living room, large granite passthrough to the kitchen, with all new granite counters, tile floors, cabinets and SS appliances. Open sight line to the dining room. Two large bedrooms on the right, both have walk-in closets and a fully renovated full bath across from the largest bdrm. Past the kitch. is a breakfast room, laundry, half-bath, access to 2-car garage. The stairs in front land on large living-space loft overlooking main floor. 2 large bedrooms up - one w/ensuite. Vaulted ceilings in the two living areas and master suite. Floor to ceiling stone fireplace wall.
